yTime":"2018-09-24T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n百里香<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>御用頂級</strong></span></span>美食評論家&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">慘過番印度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：67082851<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日唔開鋪！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">資料由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原創者</span>那吾克儉提供</span>"},{"pid":"fde81c8645d2a4cf41052c71af0c3ebd0cf41c06","tid":834201,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"30d43109fc2d995dd8851873b6040af9d19d1bd4","tid":834201,"uid":38030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"超過2個人基本已經唔使去，實冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，多人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"係 連我呢d11點幾去都已經好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6a73451b0dfa4ed353b78ad51d09fa0996190c","tid":834201,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正式宣布 呢個餐列入百里香必食套餐</span></span>"},{"pid":"6de12921b4e3255b0440c67af6db70f5137ac117","tid":834201,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"643ce8bf7ef2a9b137b4eb29eb7ff8219cf96353","tid":834201,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"印度仔有無早收?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\